{
  "content": "<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How does Manitoba business funding work?</h2>\n              <div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                  Manitoba offers a well-balanced business funding ecosystem with approximately $380 million available\n                  annually through provincial programs. The province's economic development strategy emphasizes\n                  diversification across agriculture, manufacturing, technology, and creative industries, creating\n                  broad opportunities for businesses across multiple sectors.\n                </p>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                  Manitoba's approach to business funding is notably accessible compared to larger provinces.\n                  Programs like the Manitoba Business Development Program and Innovation Growth Program offer\n                  relatively streamlined applications with reasonable processing times. The province also\n                  maintains strong support for rural economic development through dedicated programs for\n                  communities outside Winnipeg.\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"bg-teal-50 border-l-4 border-teal-500 p-4 my-6\">\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                    <strong>Key Insight:</strong> Manitoba's smaller business community means less competition\n                    for funding compared to Ontario or BC. Well-prepared applications to Manitoba programs\n                    often see approval rates 5-10% higher than national averages.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12\">What are the major Manitoba grant programs?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\">\n                {/* Manitoba Business Development */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Manitoba Business Development Program</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>$10K - $150K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>All Industries</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Manitoba's flagship business development program provides comprehensive funding for\n                      expansion, modernization, and competitiveness projects. Available to established\n                      Manitoba businesses with demonstrated operational history.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Equipment and technology modernization</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Business expansion projects</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Market development initiatives</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* Innovation Growth Program */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Innovation Growth Program</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Up to $250K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Innovation Focus</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Designed for Manitoba companies developing innovative products, services, or processes.\n                      The program supports R&D activities, technology commercialization, and innovation\n                      infrastructure development.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Research and development projects</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Technology commercialization</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Innovation infrastructure development</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* Small Business Venture Capital */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Manitoba Small Business Venture Capital</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>$50K - $500K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Growth Capital</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Manitoba's venture capital program provides equity investment for high-growth\n                      small businesses and startups. Unlike grants, this is equity financing that\n                      includes mentorship and strategic support from experienced investors.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Equity investment (not debt)</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Scale-up business support</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Strategic mentorship included</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* Rural Development Corporation */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Rural Development Corporation</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Up to $200K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Rural Focus</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Specialized support for businesses in rural Manitoba communities. This program\n                      emphasizes agricultural value-added processing, rural tourism, and community\n                      economic diversification projects.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Rural business expansion</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Agricultural processing facilities</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Community economic diversification</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Who is Eligible for Manitoba Business Grants?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                Manitoba business grants are available to for-profit enterprises operating within the province.\n                Eligibility varies by program, but most require Manitoba incorporation or significant\n                provincial operations, good tax standing, and demonstrated capacity to execute proposed projects.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Generally Eligible\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Incorporated in Manitoba or with significant Manitoba operations</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Small and medium enterprises (typically under 250 employees)</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Businesses with growth or innovation plans</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Good standing with provincial and federal tax authorities</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Projects creating economic benefit for Manitoba</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Generally Ineligible\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Businesses without Manitoba operations</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Projects completed before application</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Businesses in arrears with government</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Real estate speculation</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Franchise fees and licensing</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Much Grant Funding Can Manitoba Businesses Get?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                Manitoba grant amounts vary by program and project scope. Most programs use cost-sharing\n                models where grants cover 25-50% of eligible costs, with the business contributing the remainder.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-teal-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Program Type</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Typical Range</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Cost Share</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Micro Business Programs</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">$5K - $25K</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">50%</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Business Development</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">$25K - $150K</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">33-50%</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Innovation Grants</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">$50K - $250K</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">33-50%</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Venture Capital</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">$100K - $500K</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Equity basis</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Manitoba businesses can often stack provincial funding with\n                  federal programs like SR&ED and IRAP. Western Economic Diversification (now PrairiesCan)\n                  also provides federal funding specifically for Manitoba businesses.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How to Apply for Manitoba Business Grants - Step by Step</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-6\">\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-teal-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">1</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Research Programs (1-2 weeks)</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Visit the Manitoba Economic Development website to review active programs.\n                      Manitoba's Business Link offices in Winnipeg and regional centers offer\n                      free program matching consultations.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-teal-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">2</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Initial Consultation (Optional but Recommended)</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Most Manitoba programs offer pre-application consultations. This free service\n                      helps ensure your project aligns with program objectives before investing\n                      time in a full application.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-teal-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">3</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Prepare Application (2-3 weeks)</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Complete the application form with business plan, project description,\n                      timeline, and budget. Manitoba applications are generally shorter than\n                      other provinces—typically 10-20 pages plus supporting documents.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-teal-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">4</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Submit & Review Process</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Submit through the provincial online portal or designated intake office.\n                      Most programs have 45-90 day review timelines. Be responsive to any\n                      follow-up questions from program officers.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-teal-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">5</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Funding Agreement</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      If approved, you'll receive a contribution agreement outlining terms,\n                      milestones, and reporting requirements. Review carefully before signing.\n                      Funds typically flow on reimbursement or milestone basis.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What Documents Are Required for Manitoba Grant Applications?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center\">\n                    Core Business Documents\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Manitoba corporate registration</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>2-3 years of financial statements</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Current year-to-date financials</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Bank statements (last 6 months)</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center\">\n                    Project-Specific Documents\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Detailed project plan with milestones</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Itemized budget with vendor quotes</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Market analysis</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Letters of support (if applicable)</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Long Does Manitoba Grant Approval Take?</h2>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-teal-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Program Type</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Review Timeline</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">First Payment</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Micro Programs</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">2-4 weeks</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Upon approval</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Business Development</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">45-60 days</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">After agreement</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Innovation Grants</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">60-90 days</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Milestone basis</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Note:</strong> Most Manitoba programs accept applications on a continuous basis\n                  throughout the year. Check the official Manitoba Economic Development website for\n                  current program status and any temporary closures.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Common Mistakes to Avoid with Manitoba Grant Applications</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">1</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Underestimating Job Creation Requirements</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Many Manitoba programs heavily weight job creation. Be specific about\n                          positions, wages, and timing. Quality Manitoba jobs with competitive\n                          wages are valued over quantity.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">2</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Missing the Rural Opportunity</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Rural Manitoba programs are often less competitive than Winnipeg-focused\n                          funding. If you have operations outside the city, explore rural development\n                          programs alongside urban ones.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">3</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Not Demonstrating Matching Funds</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Manitoba programs require you to co-invest 50-75% of project costs.\n                          Applications without clear evidence of matching funds are typically rejected.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Which industries get the most Manitoba funding?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Agriculture & Agri-Food</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Value-added processing, precision agriculture, and food innovation</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Manufacturing</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Aerospace, transportation equipment, and advanced manufacturing</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Technology & Digital</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Software, fintech, and digital transformation</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Life Sciences</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Biotech, medical devices, and health innovation</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Creative Industries</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Film, media, and digital content</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Tourism</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Rural tourism and experience economy</p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Are there local grants in Winnipeg and rural Manitoba?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Winnipeg Programs</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Yes! Winnipeg – Innovation and technology hub</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>North Forge Technology Exchange – Startup programs</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Economic Development Winnipeg – Business support</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Rural Manitoba Programs</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Community Futures – Regional business support</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Rural Economic Development Initiative</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Northern Manitoba Development programs</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What if I don't qualify for Manitoba grants?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">SR&ED Tax Credits</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    Federal R&D tax credits provide 35-64% return on eligible expenditures.\n                    No provincial SR&ED match in Manitoba, but federal credits are substantial.\n                  </p>\n                  <a href=\"/blog/sred-scientific-research-experimental-development\">\n                    Learn about SR&ED →\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">PrairiesCan (Federal)</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    Federal regional development agency for Manitoba, Saskatchewan, and Alberta.\n                    Offers significant funding for innovation and economic development.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                {faqData.map((faq, index) => (\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg flex items-start\">\n                        {faq.question}\n                      </h3>\n                      <p class=\"text-gray-700 mt-2 ml-7\">{faq.answer}</p>\n                  </div>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n",
  "shortAnswer": "Yes — Complete guide to Manitoba small business grants. Access Manitoba Business Development, Innovation Growth Program, Small Business Venture Capital, and Rural Development Corporation funding. Funding available: up to $380M+.",
  "shortAnswerQuestion": "What small business grants are available in 2026?",
  "faq": [
    {
      "question": "What is the application deadline for Manitoba Small Business Grants  | + Business Development Programs in 2026?",
      "answer": "Deadlines typically vary by specific program tier. However, for 2026, many initiatives operate on a rolling intake basis until funds are depleted. Check the official portal for specific cutoffs."
    },
    {
      "question": "How much funding can I get through Manitoba Small Business Grants  | + Business Development Programs?",
      "answer": "Funding amounts range depending on business size and scope. Top awards can reach $380M."
    },
